------------------------------------------------------------
	SIVP 0.3.0
------------------------------------------------------------
features:
 + image I/O: imread, imwrite
 + image showing: imshow
 + video I/O, camera read: aviinfo, aviopen, camopen, aviclose, 
		avicloseall, avilistopened, avireadframe
 + Spatial transformation: imcrop, imresize
 + Image Arithmetic: imabsdiff

